#: en/articles/lpi-101-advanced-p4.xml:232
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You should <e>not</e> save or make any changes to a disk's partition table if\n"
"any of its partitions contain filesystems that are in use or contain important\n"
"data. Doing so will generally cause data on the disk to be lost.\n"
