#. type: Content of: <guide><chapter><section><body><ul><li>
#: en/articles/lpi-101-advanced-p4.xml:2503
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    <path>secure</path>: Authentication messages and errors, kept separate from\n"
"    <path>messages</path> for extra security\n"
